    "Critically, the raw data remains encrypted on the nodes, ensuring privacy and security during transmission.",
    "Upon receiving the model updates, the central server employs a suitable aggregation mechanism, such as weighted averaging or median selection, to amalgamate the contributions from different nodes.",
